N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 6174.5 - Consultation with the office

State Regulations

The Division shall consult with the Office regarding the
confirmation of human trafficking victims pursuant to Social Services Law, section 483-c c, including, but not limited to, the form and manner in which a
statutory referral source shall refer a person who reasonably appears to be a
human trafficking victim. Notes
